709173f-a.title: Manhattan: 5th Avenue - 86th Street
709173f-a.text:
1048-1044 Fifth AvE., at, adjoining and south of the S.E. corner of
1ast 86th Street. Also shown are Nos. 2-10 East 86th Street, adjoining and
east of said corner. Corner building is the residence of William Starr
Miller.
Prior to 1922.
Brown Brothers.
